                    </table>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="article-text"><strong>Translation:</strong> The hype machine is breaking down. No hype = no
                    momentum = no price support.</p>
                <h3 class="subsection-title">5. Valuation Exhaustion</h3>
                <p class="article-text">Even diehard bulls are tapping out. When Tesla trades at <strong>45x
                        earnings</strong> while Toyota trades at <strong>9x</strong>... even the most optimistic can't
                    justify it anymore.</p>
                <div class="example-box">
                    <div class="example-header"> <span class="example-icon">üìä</span> <span>Valuation Reality
                            Check</span> </div>
                    <div class="cheat-table">
                        <div class="comparison-table-wrapper">
